Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.09,0:00:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你在發呆就捉弄了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這反應也太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲利斯麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成你是白鯨的霧吸入過多了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這句話就已經回答了我的疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存盤點更新了麼...
